{"tid":1558711,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"在晚星墜落徬徨午夜","createTime":"2019-09-10T14:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:56:58.000Z","uid":320618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"415b943c319ece6520f0b3aaec97c8ec991ee993","tid":1558711,"uid":320618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"Design朋友整左幅靚靚文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未來會有更多~<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVqJin8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVqJin8.jpg&h=12804fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足們  難過失落嘅時候 試下回想呢三個月以來感動人心嘅場景、各種moment<br />\n幾次百萬人遊行  記唔記得我地點樣塞爆馬路？<br />\n823人鏈連上獅子山  手機燈光璀燦奪目<br />\n有幾多個香港人  就有幾多句<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">加油</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋暫時乜都未贏到<br />\n但係香港人係打不死架嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋會撐到勝利嗰一日<br />\n撐到光復家園嗰一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港  時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3dc7fbabf5e9df431d8d71647845bb637d35cdcd","tid":1558711,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:25:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"97680cf27c0e405d30f19830c303b750c78a29ea","tid":1558711,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e38001a101a9ba65a38d823457a6f8d7226ce512","tid":1558711,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正"},{"pid":"36a6907588b6a0a05b378c1b80d86b3053db9a8a","tid":1558711,"uid":320618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:44:49.000Z","msg":"有無人想要手機wallpaper<img src=\"/assets/